short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Make Top Green Search your default search in browser omnibox.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension allows you to set the Top Green Search search engine as your primary search provider in the address bar.
Top Green Search search engine is an alternative search engine with the ability to search for content in various sources with an emphasis on user privacy.

Terms of Use: https://topgreenview.com/terms.html
Privacy Policy: https://topgreenview.com/privacy.html

By click on «Add to Chrome» button and installing the Top Green Search extension, you are agreeing to install this extension, you are agreeing Privacy Policy, and you are agreeing Terms of Use.
